params.name: data.update_mask
params.description: Field mask is used to specify the fields to be overwritten in the Features resource by the update. The fields specified in the update_mask are relative to the resource, not the full request. A field will be overwritten if it is in the mask. If the user does not provide a mask then only the non-empty fields present in the request will be overwritten. Set the update_mask to * to override all fields. Updatable fields: description labels * disable_monitoring
